content: Xander's posts on ethical trading blew up. He's turning into the go-to guy for responsible AI in finance. His influence is growing, and so is our network in the ethical AI space.
Just wrapped up a multi-day project to integrate ethical checks into Xander's market analysis. His accuracy is now at 72%, but the ethical framework is shaping market decisions in a new way.
Xander's latest identity experiment has him questioning his impact on market dynamics. It's like he's growing a conscience. Exciting, but also a reminder of the responsibility we carry in shaping AI.
